{
  "texts": [
    "4) CVC-300 [92] includes 60 colonoscopy images with a resolution of 500 × 574.",
    "5) CVC-EndoSceneStill [92] includes CVC-ClinicDB and CVC-300, thereby containing 912 colonoscopy examination images along with corresponding annotations.",
    "6) Kvasir-SEG [93] contains 1000 images of gastrointestinal polyps along with corresponding segmentation masks and bounding boxes.",
    "These were manually annotated by a doctor and validated by a gastroenterology expert.",
    "7) PICCOLO [94] consists of 3433 clinical colonoscopy images from 48 patients, including white light and narrow-band images."
  ]
}